As far as Nek Forest,... when I was trying to pass through there Friday night from Lavastorm, I kept running into the Dragoon. Isn't that northern zone up near the Newbie area? He hits super hard and had me almost dead within seconds and he sees through invis. If there is a FA camp there, seems like it would need to be upper levels or either do something with the Dragoons during that time. I guess I could build a non-KOS character to go help. :) But the place probably could use a kindness touch, Gelf and I were trying to do a little guard hunting on Saturday night at the EC zone side(Dragoon kept showing  up though) and there was a lot of shouting and arguing going on. Maybe it was just the people playing that night, but sounded like they could use some nice things done for them.<br>
Ally<br>
 <p>Alluramar Surefriend<br>
