I only passed through Blackburrow (BB is for Blackburrow, right or Butcherblock?) :)  I didn't go downstairs, is it fun? Most of the gnolls ignored Gelf and I on our way through.<br>
<br>
I agree with you about Qeynos... there weren't many people there. And it is such a pretty city. I loved it there. I'm surprised that Gelf has been going back (we only get to hunt together for about an hour or so since we are on diff coasts, he goes a lot of places without me) after that debaucle a couple of weeks ago in the sewers. Thanks again to everyone who helped. I guess the money is calling to him, he's been hunting raiders in NK. Accumulating money for his 24th level, he said. We may be heading out that way with a pass through HPK, I'd like another go at the Goblin Dungeon, that was fun. And I want to get another level or two. <p>Alluramar Surefriend<br>
